        <item>
            <title>串流游戏平台可上架 App Store     Xbox Cloud Gaming、NVIDIA GeForce NOW 或受惠</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/app-store-4/software/ios-app/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=app-store-4</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/app-store-4/software/ios-app/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Pickle Rick]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 15:00:06 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[iOS App]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[App Store]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Apple]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[NVIDIA GeForce NOW]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[Xbox Cloud Gaming]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1217394</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p style="font-weight: 400;">早前，欧盟定立数位市场法（DMA），迫使苹果要改变 App Store，容许更多用户及开发者使用第三方平台开发或下载应用程式。而现时，苹果亦同意了利用 App Store 上架游戏串流服务，微软 Xbox Cloud Gaming、NVIDIA GeForce NOW 等预料将会受惠。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-medium wp-image-1217395 aligncenter" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240126at-4-694x389.png" alt="" width="694" height="389" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240126at-4-694x389.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/screenshot20240126at-4.png 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲微软 Xbox Cloud Gaming、NVIDIA GeForce NOW 预料会在 App Store 上架</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">App Store 以往存在很多限制，如只允许开发者把游戏制作成一款应用程式，限制了使用游戏串流服务。现在，开发者可以把多个游戏，制作成一款应用程式，更具自由度。虽然微软 Xbox Cloud Gaming、NVIDIA GeForce NOW 等平台制作的游戏存在限制级游戏，如 ESRB M 级。而 App Store 有年龄分级政策，届时可能会限制用户下载年龄。</p><p style="font-weight: 400;">暂时未有 Xbox Cloud Gaming、NVIDIA GeForce NOW 等平台何时会正式登上 App Store，或许需等待苹果官方消息。</p><p>资料及图片来源：<a href="https://www.windowscentral.com/gaming/apple-clears-way-for-xbox-cloud-gaming-and-nvidia-geforce-now-in-app-store">Windows Central</a></p><br /><b>相关文章:</b><blockquote><li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/17/apple-vision-pro-app-store/vr-mr-ar/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">VisionOS App Store 正式登场   Vision Pro 头戴装置专用 App 平台</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/01/microsoft-copilot-ios/software/ios-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Microsoft Copilot 人工智能工具   iOS 版程式登陆 App Store</a></li>&nbsp;<li><a href="https://unwire.hk/2023/11/30/apple-app-store-awards-2023/software/ipad-app/?utm_source=inter&utm_medium=related&utm_campaign=rp" target="_blank">Apple App Store Awards 2023 得奖名单     14 款式获奖 Apps 名单 +下载连结</a></li>&nbsp;</blockquote><br /><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/app-store-4/software/ios-app/">串流游戏平台可上架 App Store     Xbox Cloud Gaming、NVIDIA GeForce NOW 或受惠</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/app-store-4/software/ios-app/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
            <slash:comments>0</slash:comments>
        </item>
        <item>
            <title>【评测】《逆转裁判 456 王泥喜精选集中文版》　玩后感想分享</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/ace-of-attorney/game-channel/game-review/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ace-of-attorney</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2024/01/26/ace-of-attorney/game-channel/game-review/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[天恩]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 26 Jan 2024 14:00:44 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏评测]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[ace of attorney]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[逆转裁判]]>
            </category>
